g.title: Data engineers start their day by monitoring data pipelines, reviewing logs, and checking for any errors that occurred overnight.
Midday often involves collaboration with other teams, discussing data requirements, and planning for machine learning projects.
In the afternoon, data engineers focus on developing new pipelines, such as creating ones for social media data integration.
The day typically ends with data quality checks, including profiling data and addressing any quality issues discovered.
